column1: Baby Barnaby's////Baby Barnaby's was a regular on the brunch scene.  Nothing would beat rolling in slightly parched from the previous evening's events....to have a personal carafe of water and ultra-leaded coffee at the table.  My favorite order was the Huevos Rancheros sans huevos
column3: likely not the healthiest option....damn those crispy
column4: lightly seasoned breakfast potato cubes were satisfying...then they go and sprinkle some cheese on top
column5: while i mix with those zesty black beans wrapped up into a whole wheat tortilla...and PRESTO......I have returned unscathed from the Land of the Zombies.
